<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Christie Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Provincially, it is in the Calgary-West riding, represented by Ken Hughes and federally in the Calgary West riding, represented by Ron Anders.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Christie Park in in Ward 6 and represented by Richard Pootmans on the Calgary City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">South of Christie Park is Westhills Shopping Centre, with an assortment of shops, boutiques and family restaurants. Westhills also has a cinema, showing the latest movie releases. Restaurants include Montanaâ€™s, Swiss Chalet and Moxies, along with various fast food restaurants. Christie Park is home to the Islamic Centre of Calgary.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The CBE administers a public elementary in the area, with other schools in the surrounding communities.</p>
